725225f-b.title: Queens: 33rd Street - 24th Avenue
725225f-b.text:
33rd Street, west side, between 24th and Royt Avenues,
viewing south, and showing demolition for the construction,
in this area, of the Grand Central Parkway approach to the
Triborough Bridge.
View 2 is northwestward toward 33rd Street from Astoria
Boulevard.
P. L. Sperr  September 20, 1934
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
